        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Developing Responsible Individuals for a Vibrant Economy Act or the DRIVE-Safe Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to promulgate regulations to implement an apprenticeship program for licensed commercial motor vehicle drivers under the age of 21. </p>]]></text>
